rComments: Pretty good professor, class was very difficult but he graded fairly. Tests were very hard and on the long side though, and he was kind of spacey.
Pretty good teacher- he's very helpful and likes what he is doing.  Some of the quizzes and tests were pretty difficult, but he's a very fair grader.

Really good at explaining the ideas and proofs and *why* they're important, which is pretty rare among math professors.  However, is really disorganized/forgetful and often had false or bad questions on the homework and exams, or had exams that were absurdly too long.
